data.description: Introducing your new home in the heart of Hemet, CA, where comfort and style come together seamlessly. This property has recently undergone a series of thoughtful upgrades, ensuring that it's not just a house; it's a perfect home for you. Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a two-car garage featuring an upgraded automatic door, making your everyday convenience a top priority. The concrete driveway offers ample space for parking, providing an ideal place for you and your guests to leave your vehicles. For added safety and a touch of elegance, the exterior is adorned with charming lighting fixtures, illuminating your home and adding an extra layer of security. Inside, you'll discover the warmth of wood finishing in the living room, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere for relaxation and gatherings. The recently upgraded restrooms are adorned with exquisite fixtures, elevating your everyday routines to a spa-like experience. In the comfort of your bedrooms, you'll find soft and plush carpets underfoot, ensuring your days begin and end with comfort and relaxation. The recently upgraded kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern amenities and sleek finishes, making meal preparation a joy. But that's not all. The backyard is spacious enough to inspire endless possibilities. Whether you're dreaming of a potential Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU/check w city for permits) for additional space or envisioning family get-togethers in this expansive outdoor area, this property offers you the freedom to make it your own. This home is more than just a property; it's a canvas for your future memories. The recent upgrades and thoughtful features combine to provide you with a living space that's not only comfortable but also stylish and practical. Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful property your own, where the comforts of home and the potential for new adventures await.
